Author: MarceauLibrium
Title: [ANN][EQL][ICO] ⚛️ Librium - THE HYBRID FREELANCE MARKETPLACE ⚛️
Body: Glad you asked that question ashmodeus. Indeed, I think we are very different than bitjob and traditional freelance platforms.  Librium introduces the concept of a hybrid between a SaaS marketplace (App Store) and a freelance platform. What that means is that third party developers can build tools to enhance workers' skills. We call these apps the Service Providers of the ecosystem.  As an example, SparkSales.io will be the first Service Provider of the Librium Ecosystem. It provides tools (chat and AI technology) to salesmen, in order to improve the sales of e-commerce businesses. SparkSales is an existing product and business, and will drive initial value for the Librium Ecosystem.  I invite you to read more about all this in our whitepaper. And please feel free to reach out if you have any other question

Body: What is the distinguishing feature of this platform from other products on the market?

Author: MarceauLibrium
Title: [ANN][EQL][ICO] ⚛️ Librium - THE HYBRID FREELANCE MARKETPLACE ⚛️
Body: Hi Makkara,  Thanks for the question!  Yes, we have existing partnerships with digital businesses that currently use SparkSales, as well as workers. We are also establishing partnerships with third party developers and companies that would like to become new Service Providers on the Librium Ecosystem.  Moreover, we will most probably attend these two conferences in November: - World Funding Summit - consensus:invest  Quote from: klarki on November 11, 2017, 09:16:04 PM What is the distinguishing feature of this platform from other products on the market?  Traditional freelance platforms merely put workers in contact with employers. The Librium Ecosystem allows app developers to build tools that identify job opportunities. Workers are then empowered to engage those job opportunities in a manner that helps them to work more efficiently than they would have otherwise.  For example, SparkSales.io provides salesmen with chat-box technology and AI tools, allowing them to provide value that they would not be able to provide otherwise.  This is on top of the decentralized nature of the Librium Ecosystem, that allows for more efficient and lower fees transactions, a reputation system, the Librium Award System and the Librium Loan System.

Author: Sylon
Title: [ANN][EQL][ICO] ⚛️ Librium - THE HYBRID FREELANCE MARKETPLACE ⚛️
Body: Website | Whitepaper Telegram | Twitter  PRIVATE PRE-SALE STARTS NOVEMBER 8TH - 10am EST SIGN UP NOW   Built on the blockchain,  Librium unlocks a global workforce, through; (1) seamless cross border transactions enabled by cryptocurrency (2) identification of talent verified on a blockchain based reputation system, and (3) identification and  enablement of job opportunities through Service Providers - the Apps of the ecosystem. The Librium Network is designed to connect a global talent pool, including people from politically unstable regions or internet users who have difficulty receiving payment from traditional employers, with the global economy.     SparkSales.io was founded in 2016 to fill a labor shortage in an e-commerce business, and is now a successful company based in the Harvard Launch Lab, Boston.  Librium will expand on this experience and expertise to launch the Librium Ecosystem.      The Token Generation Event, taking place in December 2017, will generate up to 1 billion Librium EQL tokens. Of these, 400 million will be offered for sale during the crowdsale. The private pre-sale will start on November 8th at 10am. You can sign up now on https://librium.com      The centralized labor organization of today's world is declining, and Librium is here to bring it to an end. Decentralization is what matters, finding talent where it hides. With members coming from 3 different continents and more than 6 cities, Librium's core team is here to make a difference.     READ THE WHITEPAPER  ---------  Bounty campaign will arrive soon  ---------  PRIVATE PRE-SALE STARTS NOVEMBER 8TH - 10am EST SIGN UP NOW   Note: I am making this original post for Librium. I am not the point of contact. If you have any question, please ask it in this thread and Librium team will help you!

Author: MarceauLibrium
Title: [ANN][EQL][ICO] ⚛️ Librium - THE HYBRID FREELANCE MARKETPLACE ⚛️
Body: Thanks for your question ashmodeus. Investors in the private pre-sale have been given risk-adjusted bonuses. The target accounts for both the pre-sale AND the public crowdsale.  We don't think this will come as a problem, but if we don't reach the target, we might try a second crowdsale. If the project really does not get any traction, then buyers from the public crowdsale will of course be refunded.  Our objective here is really to build Librium in respect with our vision in the long term. Everything in our power will be done towards that goal.
